trans-unit.source: Specifies the drawing mode for a background image.

The ChartImageWrapMode enumeration represents the drawing mode for a background image, as set by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImageWrapMode%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen ChartImageWrapMode representerer tegnemodus for bakgrunnsbilde, som angitt av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImageWrapMode%2A>for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImageWrapMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: To set a background image for a chart element, use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Angi et bakgrunnsbilde for et diagramelement ved bruk av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImage%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If you specify the Unscaled value, the location where the image is drawn will depend on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImageAlignment%2A> property setting.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis du angir verdien for ikke-skalert, plasseringen der bildet tegnes avhenger av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImageAlignment%2A>egenskapsinnstillingen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart.BackImageAlignment%2A>

trans-unit.source: Background image is scaled to fit the entire chart element.
trans-unit.target: Bakgrunnsbildet skaleres tilpasses elementet hele diagrammet.

trans-unit.source: Background image is tiled to fit the entire chart element.
trans-unit.target: Bakgrunnsbildet er side ved side tilpasses elementet hele diagrammet.

trans-unit.source: Every other tiled image is reversed around the X-axis.
trans-unit.target: Hver side ved side bildet er reversert rundt x-aksen.

trans-unit.source: Every other tiled image is reversed around the X-axis and Y-axis.
trans-unit.target: Hver side ved side bildet er reversert rundt x og y-aksen.

trans-unit.source: Every other tiled image is reversed around the Y-axis.
trans-unit.target: Hver side ved side bildet er reversert rundt y-aksen.
